# Markdown table separator format

Applies to **all** Markdown tables in this project, in any file (docs, rules, README, etc.).

## Rule

Table separator rows **must** have a space between each pipe (`|`) and the dashes. No exceptions.

```markdown
❌ Wrong (no spaces — will be flagged)
|-----------|-----------|-------|

✅ Correct (space between | and dashes — required)
| --------- | --------- | ----- |
```

When creating or editing a table, always use the spaced separator row. Fix any existing tables that use the wrong format.
